-- MOVES-Mayank Parekh joins Value Partners from McKinsey
-- 
-- Mon Oct 27, 2014 05:30AM EDT
-- None



Oct 27 (Reuters) - Hong Kong-based fund management company Value Partners Group Ltd <0806.HK> appointed Mayank Parekh as director and managing partner for Asia and Demetrio Di Martino to lead telecom media technology practice in Asia.

Parekh, who was formerly a partner with McKinsey & Co, will focus on the firm's business strategy for the region. Value Partners also named Yeo Soo Ruey to lead the company's Asia wide private equity practice.